                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, V</hi> 181) I produce a certificate of Revell's former conviction at this Court—(<hi rend="italic">read—Convicted Feb.</hi> 1848, <hi rend="italic">confined three days</hi>)—he is the person.</p>
